WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.497
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.497 --> 00:00:02.440
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:03.760
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:11.120
I have some things on my heart because I've been praying about everything that the Lord has been showing me in the spirit.

00:00:11.409 --> 00:00:18.160
I have such an urgency in my spirit about the 10th of January, to pray over the 10th of January.

00:00:18.510 --> 00:00:26.759
I started going over things in my spirit, just rolling things over, just driving around today, praying in the spirit and asking the Lord, "What is it?

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:28.741
What's going on right now?

00:00:28.741 --> 00:00:33.486
" And the Lord came up with this: "Why is all this happening?

00:00:33.486 --> 00:00:38.865
" This is the question that I was asking him, but this is the answer he gave back to me.

00:00:38.865 --> 00:00:40.935
"Why is all this happening, Lord?

00:00:40.935 --> 00:00:41.840
What is going on?

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:44.120
" And he said, "Brandon, I've already showed you.

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:46.811
You are out of time.

00:00:46.811 --> 00:00:49.330
" Why are all the terrorist attacks happening?

00:00:49.330 --> 00:00:52.412
Why are things happening in New Orleans?

00:00:53.079 --> 00:00:58.422
The bottom line is we wrestle not against flesh and blood, folks.

00:00:58.422 --> 00:01:04.960
What is it that the enemy sees and has such an urgency to attack this man?

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:08.834
Is it that he is some kind of amazing leader?

00:01:08.834 --> 00:01:14.844
Yeah, he's a good leader, I believe, but there's more to it in the spirit realm of what's going on.

00:01:14.844 --> 00:01:18.351
The Lord said to me, "I'm just like Kim Clement even said.

00:01:18.351 --> 00:01:21.072
He is going to be a David.

00:01:21.072 --> 00:01:32.551
" But I want you to go back with me to some of the videos I've given in the past, because the Lord's bringing those videos and words up in me, and they're rolling around in me.

00:01:32.551 --> 00:01:43.096
When I told you I saw back from Rosh Hashanah—and I know I probably butchered that again because Sid said, "Brandon, I'm going to teach you how to speak this better.

00:01:43.096 --> 00:02:03.640
Say Rosh Hashanah," I believe is how he said to say it—the Lord told me when I saw the devil saying, "Time is up.

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:13.480
Adam's lease is up, and you must begin the seven-year tribulation.

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:18.544
" He said because the time was up.

00:02:19.576 --> 00:02:28.960
I saw this back in October whenever I heard the devil petition the Lord saying, "It's time.

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:31.360
Now is my time to have my seven years.

00:02:35.425 --> 00:02:39.920
" And I saw the Lord say, "I control time, Satan.

00:02:41.520 --> 00:03:01.348
" And I saw him say, "All I need is a sliver of time, for a day is as a thousand years to me, and a thousand years is as a day.

00:03:06.539 --> 00:03:09.940
" And he said, "All I need is nanoseconds, just fractions of a second.

00:03:10.310 --> 00:03:25.509
" And in that fraction of a second, he could stretch out that much time to have a revival.

00:03:25.509 --> 00:03:28.839
Do you see that?

00:03:28.839 --> 00:04:04.760
He showed me before I saw Jesus over America and I saw the Antichrist agenda coming because the enemy, the devil, was pushing so hard to stir this up and get this kicked off because he's ready for the seven-year tribulation to take as many people to hell with him as he can.

00:04:20.142 --> 00:04:22.502
I saw the Lord Jesus Christ standing over America and he said to me, "Brandon, who will stand in the gap for America?

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:24.960
Who will intercede for America?

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:43.390
" As I was looking out over America, I could see a massive storm that was coming, and I could see the Antichrist spirit trying to come on America.

00:04:43.390 --> 00:04:49.909
But the Lord was giving America a reprieve for a four-year window.

00:04:49.909 --> 00:05:01.245
Most people say, "Well, I see it past four years," but I've only seen four years.

00:05:01.245 --> 00:05:19.747
I saw that it would go into the next Shemitah cycle, which is until 2028, that we would have a four-year reprieve, a window to bring in a harvest.

00:05:19.747 --> 00:05:32.143
That's why Donald Trump was so important for the American people—that we would have a window for a great harvest.

00:05:32.143 --> 00:05:37.268
Yes, there will be great shakings.

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:45.160
You say, "Shakings still?

00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:46.700
" Yes, it's my word.

00:05:46.700 --> 00:05:50.199
Great shakings will come.

00:05:50.199 --> 00:06:13.150
A major shaking will come in the next four years, and we will see a financial harvest from the wealth of the wicked.

00:06:17.428 --> 00:06:42.429
I told you presents were coming, that God said he was going to honor his church, the people who are awake.

00:06:42.429 --> 00:06:57.937
So many things will take place in the next four years.

00:06:59.555 --> 00:07:06.940
But with that Antichrist agenda, the Lord's saying, "Who will intercede?

00:07:06.940 --> 00:07:15.480
Who will stand in the gap?

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:34.555
" That's what he said: "Brandon, go on YouTube and I want you to do this even more.

00:07:34.555 --> 00:07:36.501
Pray.

00:07:36.501 --> 00:07:39.720
Have a prayer channel.

00:07:41.587 --> 00:07:53.912
You will be known for prayer on the internet.

00:07:57.749 --> 00:07:58.911
" And that's what I'm doing, folks.

00:07:58.911 --> 00:08:05.920
