00:10:45.119 --> 00:10:56.760
As you see Donald Trump crack his whip, he will tame even Kim Jong Un, the little Pillsbury Doughboy.

00:10:56.760 --> 00:10:59.685
"I'm going to humble him.

00:11:17.524 --> 00:11:18.675
He has been in the way too long, and I will humble him," he says, "for he has persecuted my people, and I will humble him.

00:11:19.885 --> 00:11:31.626
" In a matter of time, I will crumble him, for he is a stench to me for what he has done.

