We take this body and thank you, Lord—this is the meal that heals, and by his stripes we are healed today.

00:44:16.851 --> 00:44:17.280
Now we thank you for the blood.

00:44:18.693 --> 00:44:34.773
You said if we confess our sins, you are faithful and just to forgive us and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:44:37.387 --> 00:44:42.850
We take this blood and we make much of the blood.

00:44:54.904 --> 00:44:55.209
We apply the blood of Jesus over us, that no weapon formed against us is going to prosper.

00:44:55.209 --> 00:45:04.319
I believe I receive divine protection over my wife, my children, and myself.

00:45:04.319 --> 00:45:12.337
Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it.

00:45:27.899 --> 00:45:36.860
It says a curse without a cause cannot stand, and I believe there's no cause because I'm under your blood.

00:45:36.860 --> 00:45:43.733
It's not about what I did; it's about what he did.

00:45:43.733 --> 00:45:48.800
He covered me and made me born again.

00:45:48.800 --> 00:46:01.786
He said he took our sins as far as the east is from the west and doesn't remember them.

00:46:01.786 --> 00:46:08.071
So we thank you that we're under the blood.

00:46:08.071 --> 00:46:17.667
You've got to stand underneath his mighty hand, for under his wings shall you trust.

00:46:17.667 --> 00:46:23.840
He is our defender, provider, healer, and savior.

00:46:23.840 --> 00:46:28.060
What can wash away my sin?

00:46:28.060 --> 00:46:33.267
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:46:33.267 --> 00:46:40.026
It's by the blood of Jesus that I'm redeemed.

00:46:40.026 --> 00:46:48.780
I take this blood right now in Jesus' name.

00:46:48.780 --> 00:46:51.371
Thank you, Lord.

00:46:58.066 --> 00:46:58.572
We enter in and worship you.

00:47:07.328 --> 00:47:08.948
We take the care out of our prayer today; we're not begging, we are believing.

00:47:08.948 --> 00:47:17.340
Everything you set out to do was finished on the cross.

00:47:24.014 --> 00:47:24.319
That blood covers us and made us white as snow.

00:47:24.319 --> 00:47:28.120
Holy Spirit, have your own way.

00:47:28.120 --> 00:47:35.520
You are the potter, I am the clay.

00:47:35.520 --> 00:47:40.284
Mold me and make me.

00:47:41.493 --> 00:47:44.049
We yield to you, Holy Spirit.

00:47:46.786 --> 00:47:48.623
We give you praise and glory.

00:47:48.623 --> 00:47:57.893
Peace, wonderful peace, coming down from the Father above, sweep over my spirit.

00:48:00.985 --> 00:48:02.845
We tap into that peace today.

00:48:09.800 --> 00:48:10.579
I keep vertical and keep my eyes upon my Father.

00:48:10.579 --> 00:48:16.520
In you, I have everything I ever need.

00:48:22.885 --> 00:48:23.820
Jesus, Jesus, Jesus, there's just something about that name.

00:48:23.820 --> 00:48:28.851
Master, Savior, Jesus, like a fragrance after the rain.

00:48:28.851 --> 00:48:37.160
Kings and kingdoms will all pass away, but there's something about your name.

00:48:39.187 --> 00:48:41.224
We trust you, Father.

00:48:41.224 --> 00:48:48.920
I'm not even worried that I might not make it through, because I trust you.

00:48:48.920 --> 00:48:53.020
I know you love me.

00:48:53.020 --> 00:48:56.360
You'll never let me down.

00:49:03.240 --> 00:49:09.367
We are not moved by what is going on; we're moved by what your Word says.

00:49:09.367 --> 00:49:14.754
We're stopping the fires before they start.

00:49:27.359 --> 00:49:28.099
Father, I keep myself centered with you.

00:49:47.880 --> 00:49:48.080
We glorify your name in all the earth.

00:49:48.080 --> 00:49:52.540
Oh, what a sweet Father you are.

00:49:52.540 --> 00:49:55.669
Lord, you're not surprised by any of it.

00:49:55.669 --> 00:50:01.051
Peace like a river, sweep over my spirit forever.

00:50:01.051 --> 00:50:21.000
You've got to come up higher and pray from his throne by taking all this junk off of you—all the bags and cares of life weighing you down.

00:50:21.000 --> 00:50:28.370
You've got to take the care out of your prayer.

00:50:28.370 --> 00:50:31.785
I have to practice this all the time.

00:50:31.785 --> 00:50:39.319
God is not moved by your need; he is moved by your faith.

00:50:39.319 --> 00:50:51.860
Find a scripture that pertains to what you are believing God for and use that in your prayer.

00:50:56.183 --> 00:51:15.355
Father, right now in the name of Jesus, I know what you've said about America and you're not done with it.

00:51:16.480 --> 00:51:28.980
We lift up President Trump and the things coming against him—the false accusations—and we bind you, Satan, in the name of Jesus.

00:51:28.980 --> 00:51:35.343
Cease and desist in your maneuvering against our president.

00:51:35.343 --> 00:51:41.370
Get your hands off of God's man.

00:51:43.010 --> 00:51:56.434
Father, I thank you that there is a mighty angelic host warring in behalf of President Trump.

00:51:56.434 --> 00:52:13.006
Get your hand off of our nation, for we intercede for the nations of this world, from Canada to Mexico to Europe to Asia.

00:52:13.006 --> 00:52:26.239
We say we will have one last revival, one last harvest of souls like this world has never seen.

00:52:28.937 --> 00:52:35.686
The Lord Jesus Christ will have his way.

00:52:40.510 --> 00:52:45.955
We will have the greatest outpouring and manifestations of glory like we've never seen before.

00:52:48.337 --> 00:52:54.360
We decree and declare that we will see this now in Jesus' name.

00:52:54.360 --> 00:53:07.260
Now, this judge in New York—we bind that spirit maneuvering in him right now causing havoc and torment.

00:53:20.869 --> 00:53:21.194
You cease and desist.

00:53:25.489 --> 00:53:26.845
You stop trying to cause drama on the 10th.

00:53:26.845 --> 00:53:35.639
We will have the Supreme Court rise up and squash this plan.

00:53:42.480 --> 00:53:47.480
Father, I thank you that you humble these judges and these people who are evil.

00:53:52.091 --> 00:53:55.410
We thank you for divine protection and healing over our nation.

00:53:56.040 --> 00:54:03.371
Father, there will be no demonic spirit that takes out our president.

00:54:13.613 --> 00:54:15.433
We hold the blood over Inauguration Day.

00:54:25.820 --> 00:54:30.719
I thank you that the 6th this time will go smoothly without people acting out.

00:54:30.719 --> 00:54:40.760
There will be a covering over our capital and there will not be any January 6th weirdness.

00:54:42.645 --> 00:54:45.450
I plead the blood of Jesus over this nation.

00:54:47.132 --> 00:54:51.064
The terrorist attacks that I've seen—we say you are brought to justice.

00:54:51.064 --> 00:54:56.880
You are found in the vans, the semi-trucks, and the dump trucks.

00:54:56.880 --> 00:55:03.690
Your plans will fall apart and there will be confusion in the terrorist camp.

00:55:04.654 --> 00:55:10.471
You will not be successful in anything trying to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:55:21.982 --> 00:55:22.613
Father, we pray over President Trump's family and over him as he plays golf—that no drones or secret stealth drones come nigh him.

00:55:22.613 --> 00:55:26.404
We plead the blood over every border.

00:55:26.404 --> 00:55:40.799
We hold the blood of Jesus over every person trying to cross, and just like Ananias and Sapphira, if it need be, they'll fall over.

00:55:40.799 --> 00:57:09.670
They will not touch our nation.

00:57:09.680 --> 00:58:30.914
We rise up spiritually like Davids and slay that giant.

00:58:30.914 --> 00:58:42.753
I thank you, Lord, for protection over our land, over football games, national championships, and the Super Bowl.

00:58:42.753 --> 00:58:54.352
Divine protection is over major sporting events, movie theaters, and megachurches.

00:58:54.352 --> 00:59:01.960
We plead the blood over every congregation—Baptists, Methodists, Catholics—every denomination.

00:59:01.960 --> 00:59:06.200
We cover them in the blood.

00:59:06.200 --> 00:59:34.450
We thank you for divine restoration over America and for the angels pairing away and putting a guard around President Trump.

00:59:34.460 --> 01:01:36.632
Every dark thing will be exposed by the light.

01:02:15.446 --> 01:02:45.468
The fertilizer will be found; the FBI, CIA, and Homeland Security will find any plot of the wicked.

01:02:45.468 --> 01:04:04.308
You are raising up men and women of God in these agencies who know how to hear your voice.

01:04:04.308 --> 01:06:16.519
Even the ones not born again will hear you and find the plots.

01:06:16.519 --> 01:06:46.678
I thank you for covering this nation.

01:06:46.678 --> 01:07:26.775
There are still great things to come.

01:07:26.775 --> 01:07:54.859
We thank you that no plague comes nigh us and that we're always in the right place at the right time.

01:07:54.859 --> 01:08:20.714
We plead the blood over the 10th, the 9th, 8th, and all the way to the 20th.

01:08:20.714 --> 01:08:28.297
Your divine protection is over Inauguration Day.

01:08:28.297 --> 01:08:52.446
Father, we pray over Canada and thank you that Justin Trudeau's days are numbered.

01:08:53.429 --> 01:09:41.706
They will have a godly leader bringing conservative thinking back over Canada, and there will be a major revival there.

01:09:41.706 --> 01:10:33.400
You are no respecter of persons, so bring change to their nation and over Europe for a great move of the spirit.

01:10:33.400 --> 01:11:21.624
We pray for every believer here, that they are healed and whole.

01:11:21.624 --> 01:11:34.060
Their marriages are strong and their wayward children are called in.

01:11:34.060 --> 01:12:41.716
Satan, get your hands off these kids and unsaved loved ones.

01:12:41.716 --> 01:15:39.978
There will be a radical move of salvation where blinded eyes open, deaf ears hear, and the paralyzed get up out of wheelchairs.

01:15:39.978 --> 01:15:57.964
I believe for a divine outflow of the spirit over all of Asia.

01:17:39.306 --> 01:17:44.399
The communistic spirit will be broken and the Iron Curtain will come down in Jesus' name.

01:19:06.326 --> 01:19:36.489
We call forth these governments trying to hold back the move of God; Father, move them out and expose the darkness.

01:19:36.489 --> 01:19:40.413
We receive everything you have for us.

01:19:40.413 --> 01:19:52.354
Now, I believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit.

01:19:52.354 --> 01:21:20.960
Acts Chapter 2 says he filled them to overflow and they began to speak with other tongues.

01:21:31.138 --> 01:21:31.766
I believe we have that gift today.

01:22:13.675 --> 01:22:15.375
I'm going to pray in the spirit for a little while and see if the Lord shows me anything.

01:22:53.280 --> 01:22:54.877
Father, we're open vessels.

01:23:49.900 --> 01:23:50.205
I thank you that you pray through me.

01:23:50.205 --> 01:23:50.510
That's interesting.

01:25:07.463 --> 01:25:11.275
I just saw someone being tormented in their mind, and the Lord is setting you free from that demonic spirit right now.

01:25:11.275 --> 01:25:27.180
Be free from hearing voices and the things tormenting you.

01:25:27.180 --> 01:26:17.038
I saw a demonic spirit wrapped around a void.

01:26:17.038 --> 01:27:17.180
Get off of their mind now in Jesus' name.

01:27:49.138 --> 01:27:51.804
I see Las Vegas again—the pyramid building with the fountains in the front.

01:27:51.804 --> 01:27:53.679
What about that hotel, Lord?

01:27:53.679 --> 01:27:55.866
Now I see an Eiffel Tower.

01:27:55.866 --> 01:28:02.420
It's about the people walking on the streets again.

01:28:02.420 --> 01:28:08.975
Now I'm on Rodeo Drive in Beverly Hills.

01:28:08.975 --> 01:28:13.328
It's the hotel there.

01:28:13.328 --> 01:28:21.300
It's about the spirit of pride and lust—the lust after things.

01:28:22.880 --> 01:28:28.910
This is attacking greed and lust and how they're choosing locations.

01:28:28.910 --> 01:28:37.594
It's about Rodeo Drive where the real wealthy are—a sign of greed and covetousness.

01:28:37.594 --> 01:28:47.079
I was taken across to New York, to a beautiful high-rise on Central Park Avenue.

01:28:47.079 --> 01:28:49.813
These are expensive condos.

01:28:50.813 --> 01:29:25.725
It looks like a glass building with a view of the park—it's a Trump building.

01:29:25.725 --> 01:29:28.773
It's about a humbling of finances.

01:29:41.747 --> 01:29:42.093
There's a jealous spirit behind it, trying to take down the American dream.

01:29:42.093 --> 01:31:18.070
And just like that, now I'm in Miami on the beach, and now Orlando and Disney.

01:31:18.070 --> 01:31:37.709
These are major tourist landmarks and big gatherings of people.

01:31:37.719 --> 01:31:39.777
Jesus, Jesus.

01:33:02.020 --> 01:33:02.560
We plead the blood.

01:33:02.560 --> 01:33:14.583
We thank you that we see what is to come and that we hear your voice.

01:33:14.583 --> 01:33:23.633
Back to the MGM Grand, the Bellagio, and the fountains.

01:33:38.354 --> 01:33:38.817
It's about the cars again.

01:33:51.239 --> 01:34:05.400
The thing about Disney is you can't get close with a car; you have to ride that monorail.

01:34:06.824 --> 01:34:10.360
I'm seeing a suicide vest again.

01:34:10.360 --> 01:34:28.972
So we call these people discovered and uncovered.

01:36:03.890 --> 01:36:11.061
We thank you that people are protected from vests and shooters at the MGM, the Bellagio, and the Delano.

01:36:11.061 --> 01:36:21.737
At the Beverly Wilshire on Rodeo, the hotel at the end, it's a landmark.

01:36:35.435 --> 01:36:35.740
I see the New York building—the Trump building on Central Park.

01:36:39.660 --> 01:36:42.530
I just saw the Statue of Liberty and what it represents.

01:36:42.530 --> 01:36:52.703
These people's minds are so deceived that they're trying to take down a symbol to make a statement.

01:36:52.703 --> 01:36:57.520
But the glory of the Lord shall rise.

01:36:59.409 --> 01:37:05.760
We could stay in that vein for a long time, but we'll take a pause.

01:37:09.159 --> 01:37:09.449
The Lord keeps revealing more.

01:37:18.473 --> 01:37:18.786
This is a period of time to pray over the whole year—it's not all at once.

01:37:18.786 --> 01:37:23.335
They've been planning this for a long time.

01:37:23.335 --> 01:37:26.560
I said they will strike and strike.

01:37:26.560 --> 01:37:35.760
These are planned events to keep people in a state of fear.

01:37:35.760 --> 01:37:38.868
What about Europe?

01:37:38.868 --> 01:37:41.097
What about France?

01:37:54.719 --> 01:37:54.919
I see the Eiffel Tower again.

01:37:54.919 --> 01:38:06.973
There's more about France and Europe to uncover.

01:38:06.973 --> 01:41:08.202
London Bridge is falling down—we call all hidden things to be revealed in London.

01:41:27.605 --> 01:41:27.910
We pray over Italy.

01:41:27.910 --> 01:41:33.664
Rome and the Vatican—the landmarks and major churches.

01:41:33.664 --> 01:41:54.091
Father, you cover these nations.

01:41:54.091 --> 01:42:03.410
Italy—I thank you that all hidden things be revealed.

01:42:03.410 --> 01:42:12.280
I see the Vatican and the massive Notre Dame.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
They're trying to make a statement.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I appreciate you all praying with me today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
There's more about Europe, but many hands make light work.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
Thousands of us are believing together that we are changing things in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Everyone say, "Amen.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
" We have the ability to call those things that be not as though they were.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Thank you for joining me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We'll be back tomorrow; I've heard "emergency call" up until the 10th.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
If you're new here, this is my assignment.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Like and subscribe to spread this gospel throughout the world.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Keep a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
God bless you all, and we'll see you again soon.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Glory to God.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Thank you, Jesus, for the manifestation of what we're praying for.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
2024 is gone and now we reach for 2025.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
We thank you, Lord, that we will thrive.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Amen, amen, amen.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Glory, glory, glory.
